incident_updates.body: Update: Multiple Fiber cuts on a submarine cable from one of our provider have been identified. Ship is already on site and repairs are ongoing. The current estimated date of resolution is 28/06/2024.
We are continuing to work on a fix for this issue.

Our technical teams are currently working with our provider to solve the incident.
Our supplier will be carry out operations to resolve the problem.

Our technical teams are currently working with our provider to solve the incident.
Update will be posted as significant progress is made.
